This paper is related to speech recognition, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning algorithms, specifically neural networks, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves signal processing techniques, which could fall under cs.SI (Signal Processing) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
